  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK437">
<l>ceyaṟpāla ceyyā tivaṟiyāṉ celva</l>
<l> muyaṟpāla taṉṟik keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of the avaricious man, who does not expend it for the purposes for which he ought to expend it will waste away and not continue.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
